(*
[
    Which plots to compare,
    What variable values to highlight,
    Values of m, t0, zeta for exact solution,
    Load type for exact solution (almost always defaultCycle()),
    Perform static comparison?,
    Perform transient comparison?,
    Type of plots to add to the figure? ('static', 'transient'),
    Overrides for default plot options?
]
*)


